Complete Remodel(2021) with 2 attached Casitas on Property on 5 ACRES. Main Home is 3230 sqft. 2 bed 2 Bath Casita 1000 sqft. Studio 350 sqft. All homes have private kitchen, living space, bed & baths. 90ft covered, tin roof patio, garden beds, fruit trees, 60x32 Carport with electric, 5 pens for animals, 1 barn, 1 tack/feed shed, 1 covered hay storage, workshop, RV gate & hook-up.  Entire home & living quarters are brand new & custom finishes. 13 ft ceilings in great room with stack stone fireplace.  Kitchen with 13 ft. island, custom hood, leathered granite, wine fridge, coffee bar, 6 burner stove with griddle & RO System.  Master with 2 closets & bath with soaker tub. Main home has 4 bed & 3 bath. All barns have electric & outdoor lights. This is one of a kind with mountain views! Huge grass yard with retaining wall
